{"id": "sos028", "name": "Audio_???_702_12_17", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Captain!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Hey!?... Lucy. Didn't I tell you to sit back and await orders?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Your expression... What's the matter? What is this place...?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\nThe target's not here. Start gathering data on the geography and environment. Take the information... take the information back.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar, you alright?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "What's going on? What happened in here?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... My father's... corpse.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "What?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "I saw his mission records... He was killed by Architects. This is where it happened...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Architects, killing people? That sort of thing, the higher-ups...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... The target's father, Colin, was my father's colleague. When I was little, he came to my house and told us the truth about what had happened, but he was taken away by A.R.C.... They must know! They've been covering it up from my mother and I all these years...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Wait a second! If Architects are dangerous, then that model we brought back last year...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "You got to notify headquarters! And the data...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "...... No!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Why not? This is an issue of safety. It falls under protocol.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "This... I...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar... you... you're not protecting that Architect, are you?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Sorry... I just think that before we get to the bottom of this, we shouldn't do that to her... I want to know exactly what their position is.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "You...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Bambi? Miss Freeze? You in there? What the hell happened?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Captain, you hear me? Just received a level S emergency command. Headquarters wants us to stop the mission immediately and head back asap.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......?\nOkay, we're coming up.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Hurry up! F***... didn't even catch the bastard and we're getting called back and forth like frigging dogs...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy, you go up first.\n... Sorry. Please trust me. If I do something unforgivable... you know what to do.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... Alright.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Damn, Bambi. How can you be so short!? You need to freaking jump just to reach!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Did headquarters mention why we're heading back?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Oh, no time for fun, huh? Something weird's going on. Miss Freeze, when you were down there, you two didn't...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Shut it.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Jackal, settle down.\nCaptain, there were no details. But something this sudden... I'm guessing the drones started attacking again and headquarters determined that it they may be affected...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Got it. Thanks, Big B. Eagle-01 squad, listen up! Report back to Node 08 immediately. We're heading out in ten minutes. Start prepping!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Ha? So that's it... Hey, don't you think he's acting weird?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Yeah. Like he's not here.\nLucy, what happened down there?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... Nothing.\nLet's get ready.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Starts]</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Hello?</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Hello? May I ask who...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin, it's me.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sagar, what's the matter?</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Um, I wanted to ask you...\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["White_Noise", "Static"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Huh? What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sa...... gar... you...... <font size=\"3.6\">AHHH!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "Object Crashes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin? What's the matter!? <font size=\"3.6\">Rin！</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Ends]</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "うわ！？……Lucy。\nその場で待機してるよう言わなかったか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "ひどい顔……何かあった？\nここはいったい……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n目標はここにはいなかった。\n地形と環境データを採集して、資料を……資料を持ち帰るぞ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar、何があった？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "本当に、何があったの。\nここで何かを見た？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……父親の……遺体を。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "任務記録を見た……父さんは……アーキテクトに殺されたんだ。\nまさに、ここで……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "アーキテクトが人を殺した？\nそんなこと上はまったく……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……目標の父親Colinは俺の父親の同僚だった。\nまだ子供の頃に家に来たこともある。\nあの時、あの人は俺たちに真実を告げようとしていたんだ……なのにA.R.C.の人間に連れて行かれた……\nあいつらは知っていたに違いない！\n知っていて……知っていたのに隠してたんだ……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "待って！\nもしアーキテクトにそんな危険が眠っているなら、去年拾ったあの……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "本部に連絡を！それから資料も……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……ダメだ！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "なぜ？\nこれは市民の安全に関わる。\nそれにプロセス的にも報告はするべき……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "いや……俺は……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar……まさか……あのアーキテクトをかばってるわけ？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "悪い……ただはっきりするまでは彼女には……まずはやつらの目的を知りたい。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "バンビ？氷の女王様？\nそこにいんだろ？\nいったいそっちで何が起きてんだ？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "隊長、聞こえるか？\nレートS指令だ。\n今すぐ任務を中断して帰って来いだと。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？\nわかった。今行く。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "早くしろよー！\nくそぉ……あのおっさんを捕まえられなかったどころかまるで犬みたいにこき使いやがって……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy先に行け。\n……悪い。でも信じてほしい。\nもし、俺がお前にとって許しがたいことをした時は……どうすればいいかわかってるだろ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……わかった。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "まじかよ！\nバンビぃ～チビにもほどがあるだろ！\nジャンプしないと届かないとかまじ？嘘だろ？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……帰還命令の理由は聞いてるか？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "うおーい！俺のことは無視かよ！反抗期か？\n氷の女王様、まさかお前ら下で……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "黙れ。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "ジャッカル。とりあえず静かにしててくれないか。\n隊長、理由については何も言ってなかった。\nでもこんな急に……これは俺の予想だが、ドローンがまた暴走を始めて、本部は脅威が高いと判断したとか……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……わかった。ビッグBありがとう。\nEagle-01に命令！我々は今すぐNode08へ帰還する！\n10分後に出発だ！整列！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "はぁ？それだけかよ……なぁ、あいつおかしくねぇ？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "同感だ。\n心ここにあらずって感じだな。\nLucy、さっき中で何があった？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……何も。\n整列だって。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>もしもし？</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>もしもし？あの……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin、俺だ。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sagar？どうしたの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "あのさ、聞きたいことが……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["White_Noise", "ノイズ"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……え？どうしたんだ？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sa……gar……！……<font size=\"3.6\">きゃあ！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "物が壊れる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin？どうした！？<font size=\"3.6\">Rin！</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話終了]</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哇！？……Lucy。不是叫你們原地待命嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你的表情……怎麼了？這個地方是……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n目標不在裡面。開始地形與環境採集，把資料……把資料帶回去。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar，你還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "到底怎麼了？你在裡面發現了什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我爸……的屍體。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "什麼？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我看了他的任務紀錄……他是被建造者殺死的，這裡就是他出事的地方……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "建造者殺人？這種事，上頭……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……目標的父親 Colin 是我爸的同僚，小時候他來過我們家，想告訴我們真相，但被 A.R.C. 的人帶走……他們一定知道！而且，這麼多年來一直瞞著我和我媽……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "等等！如果建造者具有危險性，那我們去年撿到的那台……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "得通報總部這件事！還有資料也……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……不行！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "為什麼不行？這可是安全問題，按照程序來講也該這麼做。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "這個……我……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar……你……該不會在袒護那個建造者吧？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "抱歉……我只是覺得事情沒調查清楚以前，先不要對她……我想先了解他們的立場。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？冰沙妹？你們在那裏吧？下面到底出什麼事啊？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "隊長，你聽得見我嗎？剛剛接到 S 級緊急指令，總部要我們中止任務，儘快返回。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？\n好，我們要上去了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "快啦！○的……老狐狸沒抓到，還要像條狗一樣被叫來叫去……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy 妳先吧。\n……抱歉，請信任我。如果妳判斷我做出了無法原諒的事……妳知道該怎麼做。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……好。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哇靠，斑比你怎麼可以那麼矮啊！還要用跳的才搆得到！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……總部有說明返回的理由嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哎唷，居然不理我。很反常唷？\n冰沙妹，你們該不會在下面……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "閉嘴。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "豺狼，你先安靜一下吧。\n隊長，指令裡什麼都沒說，但這麼突然……我猜想，如果無人機又發動攻擊，而且總部判斷有受波及的風險……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我知道了，謝了，大 B。\nEagle-01 小隊聽令！立即返回 Node 08，我們十分鐘後出發。大家開始整隊！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哈？就這樣……喂，你們不覺得他怪怪的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "我有同感，他好像有點心不在焉。\nLucy，剛剛在裡面到底怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……什麼事也沒有。\n開始整備吧。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>喂？</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>喂？請問是……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin，是我。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sagar？怎麼了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "那個，我想問妳……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["White_Noise", "雜訊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……唔？怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sa……gar……你……<font size=\"3.6\">呀啊！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "物品摔碎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin？怎麼了！？<font size=\"3.6\">Rin！</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대장!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "허억! ?......Lucy. 원위치로 돌아가라는 명령 못들었어?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대장 표정이...... 왜 그래? 이 곳은 대체......? \n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n타깃은 안에 없었다. 지형과 이곳 환경에 대한 데이터를 수집하고.... 다시 돌아간다.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar, 정말 괜찮은 거야?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대체 왜 그래? 안에서 뭘 본 거야? \n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......아버지의......시신.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "뭐?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아버지의 임무 기록을 봤어... 아키텍트에게... 살해당했어. 이곳이 바로 아버지가 임무를 수행했던 장소...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "아키텍트가 살인을? 그런 일이라면, 곧바로 상부에게 보고를...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......타깃의 부친, Colin은 내 아버지의 동료였어. 어렸을 때 우리집에 오신 적이 있었지. 그때 내게 진실을 말해주려고 했었어. 하지만 A.R.C. 사람들이 그를 데리고 가버렸어... 그들은 분명 뭔가를 알고 있었어! 게다가... 이렇게 오랜 시간 나와 어머니에게도 그 사실을 숨기고 있었던 거야...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "잠깐! 만약 아키텍트가 위험성을 지닌 존재라면, 우리가 작년에 주웠던 그 기체도...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......! \n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "당장 본부에 이 사실을 알려야해! 그리고 데이터 역시...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......안 돼!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "어째서? 이건 안전과 직결된 문제라고. 메뉴얼대로라면 그렇게 하는 것이 맞는 거잖아.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "그건.......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar......설마......그 아키텍트 때문에 이러는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "미안...... 정확한 조사 결과가 나오기 전에는 그 애한테... 먼저 윗 사람들의 입장을 들어봐야겠어.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대장......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "밤비? 얼음 여왕? 그 안에 있는 거야? 아래서 대체 무슨 일이 벌어진 거야?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "대장, 내 목소리 들려? 방금 S레벨의 긴급 명령이 떨어졌어. 즉시 임무를 중단하고 복귀하라고.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......? \n알았다. 우리도 이제 올라갈 거야.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "서두르라고! x발...... 늙은 여우 새끼도 못잡고, 여기 저기 뛰어다니며 개고생만 했네...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy, 먼저 가.\n......미안하다. 날 믿어줘. \n만약 내가 용서받을 수 없는 일을 행하려고 한다면... 그땐... 어떻게 해야하는지 알고 있겠지?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......알았어.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "제길! 밤비, 네 녀석 밥이라도 좀 많이 먹지! 네가 높게 뛰어야만 내가 잡을 수 있다고!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": ".....왜 복귀하라고 명령을 내린 거지?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "야! 내 말 무시하냐... 뭔가 수상해...?\n얼음 여왕, 너희들 설마 아래에서...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "닥쳐.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "울프, 너부터 좀 조용히 해.\n대장, 별다른 말은 없었어. 그래도 이렇게 갑자기.....내 예상이지만, 드론이 또 폭주를 시작했고, 본부는 위협이 높다고 판단해서 그랬다든지...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......알겠다. 고마워, B.\nEagle-01 소대 주목! 즉시 Node 08로 복귀한다! 10분 뒤 출발이니 채비하도록!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "하아? 그게 다야...? 야, 너희들 뭔가 저녀석 이상하다고 생각하지 않아?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "동감이다. 뭔가 저 녀석 답지 않아.\nLucy, 방금 대체 안에서 무슨 일이 있었던 거지?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......아무일도 없었어.\n출발 채비나 해.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 시작]</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>여보세요? </i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>여보세요? 누구...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin, 나야.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sagar? 무슨 일이에요?</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "저기... 네게 물어볼 게 있어......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["White_Noise", "노이즈"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......큭! 왜 이러지?\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sa......gar......!......<font size=\"3.6\">꺄악! </font></i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "물건이 부서진다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin? 왜 그래! ? <font size=\"3.6\">Rin！</font>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 종료]</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哇！？……Lucy。不是叫你們原地待命嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你的表情……怎麼了？這個地方是……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n目標不在裡面。開始地形與環境採集，把資料……把資料帶回去。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar，你還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "到底怎麼了？你在裡面發現了什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我爸……的屍體。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "什麼？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我看了他的任務紀錄……他是被建造者殺死的，這裡就是他出事的地方……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "建造者殺人？這種事，上頭……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……目標的父親 Colin 是我爸的同僚，小時候他來過我們家，想告訴我們真相，但被 A.R.C. 的人帶走……他們一定知道！而且，這麼多年來一直瞞著我和我媽……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "等等！如果建造者具有危險性，那我們去年撿到的那台……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "得通報總部這件事！還有資料也……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……不行！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "為什麼不行？這可是安全問題，按照程序來講也該這麼做。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "這個……我……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar……你……該不會在袒護那個建造者吧？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "抱歉……我只是覺得事情沒調查清楚以前，先不要對她……我想先了解他們的立場。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？冰沙妹？你們在那裏吧？下面到底出什麼事啊？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "隊長，你聽得見我嗎？剛剛接到 S 級緊急指令，總部要我們中止任務，儘快返回。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？\n好，我們要上去了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "快啦！○的……老狐狸沒抓到，還要像條狗一樣被叫來叫去……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy 妳先吧。\n……抱歉，請信任我。如果妳判斷我做出了無法原諒的事……妳知道該怎麼做。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……好。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哇靠，斑比你怎麼可以那麼矮啊！還要用跳的才搆得到！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……總部有說明返回的理由嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哎唷，居然不理我。很反常唷？\n冰沙妹，你們該不會在下面……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "閉嘴。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "豺狼，你先安靜一下吧。\n隊長，指令裡什麼都沒說，但這麼突然……我猜想，如果無人機又發動攻擊，而且總部判斷有受波及的風險……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我知道了，謝了，大 B。\nEagle-01 小隊聽令！立即返回 Node 08，我們十分鐘後出發。大家開始整隊！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["St