tion", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n目标不在里面。开始地形与环境采集，把资料……把资料带回去。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar，你还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "到底怎么了？你在里面发现了什么吗？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我爸……的尸体。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "什么？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我看了他的任务纪录……他是被建造者杀死的，这里就是他出事的地方……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "建造者杀人？这种事，上头……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……目标的父亲 Colin 是我爸的同僚，小时候他来过我们家，想告诉我们真相，但被 A.R.C. 的人带走……他们一定知道！而且，这么多年来一直瞒着我和我妈……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "等等！如果建造者具有危险性，那我们去年捡到的那台……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "得通报总部这件事！还有资料也……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……不行！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "为什么不行？这可是安全问题，按照程序来讲也该这么做。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "这个……我……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Sagar……你……该不会在袒护那个建造者吧？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "抱歉……我只是觉得事情没调查清楚以前，先不要对她……我想先了解他们的立场。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？冰沙妹？你们在那里吧？下面到底出什么事啊？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "队长，你听得见我吗？刚刚接到 S 级紧急指令，总部要我们中止任务，尽快返回。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？\n好，我们要上去了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "快啦！ ○的……老狐狸没抓到，还要像条狗一样被叫来叫去……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy 妳先吧。\n……抱歉，请信任我。如果妳判断我做出了无法原谅的事……妳知道该怎么做。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……好。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哇靠，斑比你怎么可以那么矮啊！还要用跳的才构得到！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……总部有说明返回的理由吗？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哎唷，居然不理我。很反常唷？\n冰沙妹，你们该不会在下面……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "闭嘴。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "豺狼，你先安静一下吧。\n队长，指令里什么都没说，但这么突然……我猜想，如果无人机又发动攻击，而且总部判断有受波及的风险……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我知道了，谢了，大 B。\nEagle-01 小队听令！立即返回 Node 08，我们十分钟后出发。大家开始整队！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "哈？就这样……喂，你们不觉得他怪怪的吗？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "我有同感，他好像有点心不在焉。\nLucy，刚刚在里面到底怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……什么事也没有。\n开始整备吧。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话开始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>喂？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>喂？请问是……？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Rin，是我。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rin]"], "content": "<i>Sagar？怎么了吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "那个，我想问妳……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["White_Noise", "杂讯"], "content": ""},